# Password Strength Checker 🔐

This is my science fair project created by **Vullnet Grajçevci**.  
It checks how strong your password is and gives suggestions to make it more secure.

## Features
- Rates password strength from Very Weak → Very Strong
- Shows a progress bar with color coding
- Suggests improvements for better security
- Option to show/hide password

